infoModal.heading: What is star rating?
infoModal.body: The star rating tool can be helpful during the candidate assessment process. The function allows multiple users to rate the different candidates in stars (1 - 5) independently from each other. The system will then calculate the average score along with some basic statistics to make it easier to keep overview of the applicants.
